5000|$|DEFCON (stylized as DEFCOИ and {{sometimes}} subtitled Everybody Dies) is a real-time strategy game created by independent British game developer Introversion Software, developers of Darwinia, Multiwinia, Uplink, and Prison Architect. The gameplay {{is reminiscent of}} the [...] "big boards" [...] that visually represented <b>thermonuclear</b> <b>war</b> in films such as Dr. Strangelove, Fail-Safe, and especially WarGames.|$|E
